<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٦٦١ - وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/442">أَحْمَدُ بْنُ شَبِيبِ بْنِ سَعِيدٍ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2736">أَبِي </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1716">خَالِدِ بْنِ أَسْلَمَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«خَرَجْنَا مَعَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ عُمَرَ فَقَالَ:</span> هَذَا قَبْلَ أَنْ تُنْزَلَ الزَّكَاةُ، فَلَمَّا أُنْزِلَتْ جَعَلَهَا اللهُ طُهْرًا لِلْأَمْوَالِ»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>